---
title: Harissa Prawn Orzo with Garlicky Beans
description: Looking for a simple showstopper you can rustle together in just twenty-five minutes? Look no further. The African blend of Harissa is no ordinary spice mix, which is exactly why it’s the hero ingredient in tonight’s recipe. A crunchy mix of green beans and juicy prawns works beautifully with orzo.
